## Summary: Key Implementation Patterns

| Aspect | Pattern |
|--------|---------|
| **Plugin ID** | Lowercase, unique (e.g., "irc", "matrix", "nostr") |
| **Chat Types** | "direct" and/or "group" arrays in capabilities |
